00:14:17.795 --> 00:14:20.275
take a class or read a book or

00:14:20.275 --> 00:14:22.755
even just look something up and find that

00:14:22.755 --> 00:14:24.835
a short time later we have retained almost

00:14:24.835 --> 00:14:28.675
nothing. But sometimes things seem to stick. Why

00:14:28.675 --> 00:14:32.950
