00:42:13.980 --> 00:42:15.900
it for us. And then they come back

00:42:15.900 --> 00:42:19.180
3x over time, 3x over budget, one third

00:42:19.180 --> 00:42:21.420
x quality. Why is software so hard? Why

00:42:21.420 --> 00:42:24.035
can't we just tell the system what we

00:42:24.035 --> 00:42:26.995
want and get the thing out the other

00:42:26.995 --> 00:42:29.235
side? And it turns out we actually do

00:42:29.235 --> 00:42:31.875
have that kind of technology. It's called formal

00:42:31.875 --> 00:42:33.635
modeling. We've had it for a long time.

00:42:33.955 --> 00:42:35.235
